"Darling, this is love"

571
01:22:10,709 --> 01:22:14,770
"You didn't care to turn around..."

572
01:22:15,380 --> 01:22:18,349
"but I was still waiting"

573
01:22:20,152 --> 01:22:24,350
"By the time I wanted
to stop you..."

574
01:22:25,157 --> 01:22:28,092
"you were too far away"

575
01:22:29,294 --> 01:22:32,957
"What happened?
- I don't even know"

576
01:22:34,166 --> 01:22:37,693
"Why is my heart...
- In love...?"

577
