"Darling, this is love"

582
01:23:36,795 --> 01:23:40,856
"Oh time! Stop, tarry..."

583
01:23:41,666 --> 01:23:44,635
"go backwards"

584
01:23:46,271 --> 01:23:50,298
"I've left myself behind..."

585
01:23:51,276 --> 01:23:54,040
"at the crossroads of life"

586
01:23:55,280 --> 01:23:58,909
"Where am I...?
- Where are you?"

587
01:24:00,118 --> 01:24:03,645
"What is this...?
- Magic"

588
